mega: See the lights rearranging themselves around you? That's the algorithm. It's learning you.
mega: It watches when you slow down, when you almost walk away — and that's exactly when it hands you a "bonus," a free spin, a near-win to reel you back.
mega: It knows your payday. It knows your weak hours. It was trained on millions of people who lost everything, so it would know precisely how to make you lose too.
